## 🔐 Security Best Practices

* Create separate VPCs for development, staging, and production environments.
* Apply meaningful tags for governance and cost tracking.
* Use private subnets for databases and internal services.
* Avoid deploying production resources into the default VPC.
* Plan your IP addressing strategy before creating subnets.

