## ⚠️ Common Mistakes

* ❌ Using the default VPC for production workloads
* ❌ Not planning network architecture before deployment
* ❌ Forgetting to enable DNS support when required
* ❌ Applying inconsistent or missing resource tags
* ❌ Creating overlapping IP ranges that complicate future networking

